Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • production.Product
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Item
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AudioPlayer, MoviePlayer, Widget

    public abstract class Product
extends java.lang.Object
implements Item
    Abstract class that implements Item and represents a Product that can be produced. All items produced are types Product.
